HEADWORD: Ad hominem
<hw>Ad hom"i*nem</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <ety>[L., to the man.]</ety>
<def>A phrase applied to an appeal or argument addressed to the
principles, interests, or passions of a man.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

